<title>
Engine Switch Inspection
</title>
<ptxt>
<intxrefpoff refid = "AENAP70AA506015">Engine Switch Removal and Installation</intxrefpoff>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Check engine switch for continuity between terminals at each switch position.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
If check result is not as specified, replace engine switch.
</ptxt>
<attention3>
<ptxt>
Use diode range of circuit tester when checking terminals “9” and “8”.
</ptxt>
</attention3>
